All Implemented Interfaces:
Aware, InitializingBean, ResourceLoaderAware
@ImportRuntimeHints(org.springframework.boot.autoconfigure.sql.init.SqlInitializationScriptsRuntimeHints.class) public class SqlDataSourceScriptDatabaseInitializer extends DataSourceScriptDatabaseInitializer
DataSourceScriptDatabaseInitializer for the primary SQL database. May be registered as a bean to override auto-configuration.
